  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TolE040">
<l>uruviṉu micaiyiṉu arukit tōṉṟu</l>
<l>moḻikkuṟip pellā meḻutti ṉiyalā</l>
<l>vāyta maḵkāk kālai yāṉa</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though an <foreign xml:lang="ta">āytam</foreign> of lengthened duration may occur,</l>
<l>rarely, in onomatopoetic words which denote shape</l>
<l>and sound, it should not be represented in writing</l>
          <l>[as lengthened].<note place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">Iḷamp.</foreign> gives <foreign xml:lang="ta">kaẖṟu</foreign> ' darkness ' (as illustr. ' of shape ') and <foreign xml:lang="ta">cuẖṟu</foreign> ' noise produced by the movement of palmyra leaves ' (as illustr. ' of sound ').</note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
